### Windows
# Windows thumbnail cache files
Thumbs.db

# Folder config file
[Dd]esktop.ini

# Recycle Bin used on file shares
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# Windows shortcuts
*.lnk

### Agentheim dashboard runtime
# Sole runtime state on disk (pid/port runfile); never committed. See ADR-0002.
.agentheim/.dashboard/

### Agentheim dashboard build tooling
# esbuild + framework deps are BUILD-TIME only (ADR-0003); never committed.
# The committed artifacts are dashboard/dist/, build.mjs, package.json (+ lock).
dashboard/node_modules/